Anything will do.

486
00:34:55,770 --> 00:34:57,980
Why?

487
00:34:57,980 --> 00:34:59,650
Why?

488
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:06,350
For the level test.
To see how good your English is.

489
00:35:07,850 --> 00:35:09,910
Does that sound too obnoxious?

490
00:35:17,020 --> 00:35:19,930
I wanted to know what your English style was like.

491
00:35:19,930 --> 00:35:21,850
As a reference.

492
00:35:29,710 --> 00:35:32,840
Park Yeong Bae, I'm going home.

493
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:34,750
Work hard.

494
00:35:34,750 --> 00:35:39,750
Wait.
You speak a little English, don't you?

495
00:35:39,750 --> 00:35:40,890
Of course.

496
00:35:40,890 --> 00:35:43,830
Then could you help me with an English composition?

497
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:47,820
Yeah. Dad did?

498
00:35:47,820 --> 00:35:49,610
Wait!

499
00:35:53,140 --> 00:35:55,000
What's with him?

500
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:00,670
Choi Joon Woo.

501
00:36:00,670 --> 00:36:02,720
Choi Joon Woo.

502
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:07,030
Choi Joon Woo.

503
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:10,870
Ah, how do I do this English paper?

504
00:36:13,230 --> 00:36:15,250
Choi Joon Woo.

505
00:36:36,490 --> 00:36:38,270
Ma Hui Yeong?

506
00:36:39,030 --> 00:36:41,180
Choi Joon Woo?

507
00:36:48,270 --> 00:36:50,320
Welc—

508
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:53,880
Is it going well?
The free talking preparation?

509
00:36:56,850 --> 00:36:58,990
Sort of.

510
00:36:58,990 --> 00:37:01,900
Sort of won't do.

511
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:04,210
Yoo Soo Bin's English is at the top level.

512
00:37:04,210 --> 00:37:08,370
If her grades, her English,
and her exams are ruined because of you,

513
00:37:08,370 --> 00:37:10,860
how are you going to be responsible for that?

514
00:37:14,700 --> 00:37:17,000
I'll have to make it so that I don't ruin it.

515
00:37:18,650 --> 00:37:21,780
